message:
Hey ya'll, I know it's kind of early to be thinking about next school year already (sorry) but I have this really cool thing you might want to be a part of. 
Many of you participated in the Unlimited Dance Marathon this past April but UDM is looking for more to join the team!
Next year I will be serving as the Student Group Outreach Chair (aka doing this). If you want to be a part of a group who makes a huge difference for children and their families, in such an easy and seemingly small way -- please take the time to fill out this form and you can check out the Facebook page and like it below.

Hope everyone is having a fantastic summer! 

Google Form -- https://docs.google.com/a/umn.edu/forms/d/1QcYCeJ93IViRK_X4zK_mNSLsrnlUqem-duScht-_-yo/viewform?c=0&w=1

Page Link -- https://www.facebook.com/UMNdancemarathon/
